<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.8">
<l>eṉṉa tāvi mēlaiyā yērko ḷēḻu lakamum</l>
<l>tuṉṉi muṟṟu mākiniṉṟa cōti ñāṉa mūrttiyāy</l>
<l>uṉṉa teṉṉa tāviyu meṉṉa tuṉṉa tāviyum</l>
<l>iṉṉa vaṇṇa mēniṉṟā yeṉṟu raikka vallēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are on my soul, you the form of luminous knowledge</l>
<l>that stand as all, being joined to all the seven beautiful worlds,</l>
<l>“you stand in a way such that my soul is your’s</l>
<l>[and] your soul I mine”, thus I can say.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
